- cs.EM (Embedded Systems) is likely because the paper focuses on embedded system applications and platforms. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is likely because the paper proposes a runtime scheduler to optimize system performance and memory footprint. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible because the paper discusses DNNs as a workload for integrated CPU/GPU platforms.
